Data Acquisition Step (nanobrain.library.workflows.viral_protein_analysis.steps.data_acquisition_step)

BV-BRC Data Acquisition Step (Steps 1-7)

Implements the first 7 steps of the Alphavirus workflow: 1. Download all Alphavirus genomes from BV-BRC 2. Filter genomes by size (8KB-15KB range) 3-4. Extract unique protein MD5s and deduplicate 5. Get feature sequences for MD5s 6. Get annotations for unique MD5 sequences 7. Create annotated FASTA file

Based on BV-BRC CLI documentation: https://www.bv-brc.org/docs/cli_tutorial/cli_getting_started.html
